Mortgage News Daily is a news and social media website serving the mortgage, and real estate housing industries. The website serves over 50,000 members, combining the housing industry with a social media platform.
As a result of the collaborative nature of the website, Mortgage News Daily has a large consumer audience. Consumers visiting the website can ask housing related questions or search a library of previously answered questions. Submitted questions are answered by industry professionals. The result is a library of thousands of housing related answers.
